dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Trempealeau_Roads_2015.gdb. [Road centerlines for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin. Attributes are based on NENA standards and are MSAG valid where applicable.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://tremplocounty.com/landrecords/default.htm. [Whenever data is updated the metadata is manually updated. This is a QA/QC procedure in order to determine the last update of the dataset.]
